title: Butterhead Greens Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual cafe, order at counter. Many different salads that can be made vegan. Has quinoa salad and sweet potato salad for sides, a thai style entree salad (the dressing that thai style comes with is not vegan but can be substituted). House-made veggie patties is vegan suitable and may be ordered as add-on to a salad. Could build your own salad and sandwiches.
